{
  "stem": "27129.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was a river-- Bug.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And River Bug, we had to cross the River Bug.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But there was a little town where you didn't have to cross the River Bug.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Somehow, I don't remember how it was that you could get around it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So that was our destination, which the train was going there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So once we arrived at the station, you know, the name of the city was Malkin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was about 10 or 11 o'clock in the evening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So the Germans started shooting as soon as the train stopped, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They started shooting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We saw fire from all sides.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Then the Germans started hollering to disembark the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And right away, as soon as we got out of the train, they said, Jews to the right and Poles to the left.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So anyway, we tried to-- not to go to the right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We tried to go to the left, but they took those lanterns, those railroaders, you know, were using, you know, at night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they were shining in everybody's faces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And if they recognized a Jew, they beat them up and they had German shepherds with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "You know, they were tearing them to pieces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a tragedy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They recognized my brother because he was light complected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was running already to-- to the right, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was going-- you know, I didn't want to be left alone because I wanted to be with my brother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Jews were to the right you say?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to the left first, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, when they recognized my brother, they started beating on him so he was running, and the dogs after him.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
